title: Trump Repeals Landmark Climate Finding That Greenhouse Gases Endanger Public Health | 10 News
description: The Trump administration has repealed the scientific finding that greenhouse gas emissions endanger human health, removing the legal basis for climate regulations in the United States. The 2009 finding meant the Environmental Protection Agency could limit heat-trapping pollution from vehicles, power plants and other industrial sources.
